title: Long-lost African masterpiece found in London flat
text:
Long-lost African masterpiece found in London flat Thursday, February 08, 2018 - 01:40 
A portrait of a Nigerian princess that was lost for more than 40 years has been rediscovered in a flat in London. It will now be sold at auction. Anna Bevan reports
